videos.description: Ohio State works the ball around to get Duane Washington open and he knocks down the corner 3-pointer to extend the Buckeyes' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Washington gets the much needed 3 for OSU) 2019/12/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington gets the much needed 3 for OSU

videos.description: Ohio State's Luther Muhammad crosses over his defender, gets down low and feeds it to Kaleb Wesson, who slams it down.
